{"tid":2321984,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黃又南父親因病離世 喪禮因疫情低調處理","createTime":"2020-12-12T03:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T17:47:00.000Z","uid":130626,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a04c9204c37106703033c4f1b811b7d9b4e84562","tid":2321984,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T03:10:23.000Z","msg":"黃又南的爸爸黃文藻患有腦退化症，曾試過失蹤2次。一向孝順的黃又南，為了讓爸爸得到最好的照顧，早年忍痛將他送入護理院，雖然經過多年來的悉心照顧，但黃又南剛在社交網站中透露黃父已因病離世，而因為武漢肺炎疫情關係，黃又南希望低調處理爸爸的身後事。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201211/IQXZG6MN5NDGBMH5CW3QYXJKOI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201211%2FIQXZG6MN5NDGBMH5CW3QYXJKOI%2F&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmk9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=ad8e7911\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201211%2FIQXZG6MN5NDGBMH5CW3QYXJKOI%2F&h=eee88579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201211/IQXZG6MN5NDGBMH5CW3QYXJKOI/</a>"},{"pid":"0aaa79a368e5daaeeaed2eda9200336e3dced7e0","tid":2321984,"uid":192409,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T03:12:43.000Z","msg":"又黃又藍 牆頭草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029f0ab1c01e80b203b8e674b2ea1420d0aede27","tid":2321984,"uid":155012,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T03:14:01.000Z","msg":"底啦"},{"pid":"d2e5e1f9e49be0ba5cb827c009b69876318410ee","tid":2321984,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T03:16:18.000Z","msg":"又話佢老豆爭人好多錢？？？<br />\n<br />\n咁突竟係爭人好多錢先死定死左先爭人錢<br />\n<br />\n點都好，一路好走🙏"},{"pid":"df782c195b3feb5ac9ec626a7fc8fb5293a49d4b","tid":2321984,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d2e5e1f9e49be0ba5cb827c009b69876318410ee","tid":2321984,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T03:16:18.000Z","msg":"又話佢老豆爭人好多錢